These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
There 7 different types of food: apple, apricot, kiwi, pineapple, radish, raspberry, spinach
The people have 7 different hobbies: skydiving, hiking, gardening, photography, camping, reading, writing
 1. the person eating kiwi is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating pineapple is not the person who's hobby is reading##6
 3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 5. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
 7. the person eating raspberry is somewhere between the person eating apricot and the person who's hobby is hiking##7
 8. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 9. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere between the person eating radish and the person who's hobby is gardening##7
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
11. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left##1
12. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##5
13. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the right of the person eating raspberry##5
14. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the right of the person eating radish##5
15. the person eating radish is the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Food          | kiwi    | apple    | apricot | raspberry | pineapple | radish    | spinach |
| Hobby   | camping | skydiving | gardening  | reading   | photography    | hiking | writing |

