.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: weightlifting, soccer, lacrosse, sailing, biathlon, basketball, rugby
The people have 7 different hobbies: camping, chess, gardening, hiking, rock-climbing, singing, skydiving
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is soccer##7
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is chess##7
 6. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's hobby is gardening##7
 7. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is soccer##7
 8. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5
11. the person who's hobby is singing is not the person who's sport is rugby##6
12. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
13. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's sport is sailing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Sport    | rugby  | lacrosse | basketball | sailing | weightlifting     | biathlon | soccer  |
| Hobby   | gardening | singing | chess  | skydiving  | rock-climbing | hiking      | camping |

