.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-3::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: light-blue, red, blue, coral, ebony, black, chestnut
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: ambient, blues, country, d&b, hip-hop, jazz, metal
 1. the fan of metal is between the person who likes blue and the fan of country##2
 2. the person who likes red is somewhere to the right of the fan of blues##5
 3. the fan of blues is not the person who likes coral##6
 4. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5
 5. the fan of ambient is between the fan of jazz and the person who likes ebony##2
 6. the fan of country is somewhere to the right of the person who likes coral##5
 7. the person who likes chestnut is on the far right##1
 8. the person who likes coral is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
 9. the person who likes blue is somewhere between the fan of hip-hop and the fan of metal##7
10. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
11. the person who likes ebony is in an even position##4
12. the person who likes ebony is not the fan of ambient##6
13. the person who likes black is somewhere between the person who likes red and the person who likes ebony##7
14. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the person who likes ebony##3
15. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the person who likes ebony##3
16. the person who likes ebony is not the fan of jazz##6
17. the person who likes coral is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
18. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
19. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the left of the fan of hip-hop##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |    4    |       5       |     6     |      7      |
| Color         | light-blue | red | black | ebony  | blue | coral | chestnut |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | jazz       | ambient   | hip-hop | d&b           | metal     | country     |

