The people use 7 different means of transport: jet-ski, quad-bike, scooter, skateboard, snowmobile, trike, van
 1. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
 2. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
 3. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5
 4. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
 5. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching romance movies##5
 6. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is somewhere between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the snowmobile##7
 8. the person watching drama movies is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
10. the person watching horror movies is in an even position##4
11. the person watching horror movies is somewhere between the person watching time-travel movies and the person watching mystery movies##7
12. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the person watching romance movies##5
13. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
14. the person watching family movies is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5
15. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
16. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
17. the person driving the skateboard is between the person watching horror movies and the person driving the trike##2
18. the person watching time-travel movies is not the person driving the van##6
19. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2    |     3     |     4      |     5      |    6    |    7     |
| Movie-Genre       | drama | superhero    | family   | romance | time-travel     | horror  | mystery |
| Transport   | snowmobile    | scooter | quad-bike | trike      | skateboard | jet-ski | van      |

