 9. the french is not the person watching superhero movies##6
10. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the left of the chinese##5
11. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching romance movies##5
12. the person watching mystery movies is the american##1
13. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
14. the person watching documentary movies is the spanish##1
