 8. the person traveling to boston is not the australian##6
 9. the thai is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
10. the person traveling to new-york is not the australian##6
11. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person traveling to liverpool##3
12. the thai is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3
13. the chinese is not the person traveling to liverpool##6
14. the thai is the person traveling to new-york##1
15. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere to the right of the thai##5
