.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-7::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  analyst, architect, firefighter, manager, mechanic, scientist, writer
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: june, october, may, february, august, november, december
 1. the person who's birthday is in august is not the mechanic##6
 2. the scientist is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in december is the manager##1
 4. the mechanic is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere between the mechanic and the writer##7
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 8. the analyst is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
 9. the mechanic is not the person who's birthday is in february##6
10. the architect is in an even position##4
11. the architect is not the person who's birthday is in august##6
12. the person who's birthday is in december is in the middle##1
13. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who's birthday is in august and the firefighter##2
14. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere between the manager and the person who's birthday is in may##7
15. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the left of the scientist##5
16. the writer is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2     |     3     |    4    |     5      |     6     |     7      |
| Job         | firefighter | scientist | analyst   | manager | mechanic   | architect | writer     |
| Birthday   | october        | may      | august | december     | november | june  | february |

