 3. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3
 4. the person eating strawberry is the person eating strawberry##1
 5. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 6. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere between the person driving the tram and the person driving the subway##7
 7. the person eating lemon is in an odd position##4
 8. the person driving the subway is in an even position##4
 9. the person eating mango is the person driving the airplane##1
10. the person eating strawberry is between the person eating raspberry and the person driving the helicopter##2
11. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
12. the person driving the helicopter is in the middle##1
13. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
14. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
15. the person eating mango is on the far left##1
16. the person eating mango is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5
17. the person eating blueberry is somewhere to the right of the person driving the subway##5
18. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the right of the person eating zucchini##5

