.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-16::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, handball, skiing, snowboarding, swimming, tennis
7 different pets are kept: turtle, chinchilla, goldfish, hamster, rabbit, goat, fish
 1. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the hamster##7
 2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
 3. the owner of the fish is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5
 5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 6. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 7. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
 8. the owner of the goat is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 9. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
10. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
11. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
12. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
13. the owner of the turtle is somewhere between the person who's sport is skiing and the owner of the hamster##7
14. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the owner of the chinchilla##1
15. the owner of the fish is the person who's sport is cricket##1
16. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
17. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##5
18. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

