.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-17::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, chess, collecting, cooking, dancing, woodworking
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: rugby, soccer, badminton, rowing, cricket, ice-hockey, swimming
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
 2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 3. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's sport is swimming##7
 4. the person who's hobby is board-games is not the person who's sport is badminton##6
 5. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is cricket##5
 6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 7. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##5
 8. the person who's sport is cricket is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's sport is rugby is not the person who's hobby is card-games##6
11. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
12. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left##1
13. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not the person who's sport is swimming##6
14. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
15. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4
16. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
17. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's sport is badminton##7

.:: Answer ::.
