 3. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the american##3
 4. the nigerian is on the far left##1
 5. the fan of reggae is not the mexican##6
 6. the fan of country is somewhere to the left of the fan of dubstep##5
 7. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the turkish##3
 8. the fan of blues is on the left of the mexican##1
 9. the colombian is on the left or right of the american##3
10. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the fan of country##5
