12. the turkish is in an even position##4
13. the american is not the fan of d&b##6
14. the nigerian is the fan of d&b##1
15. the pakistani is not the fan of blues##6
16. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the fan of reggae##5
17. the fan of blues is somewhere between the pakistani and the mexican##7
18. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the right of the fan of dubstep##5
