 6. the indonesian is somewhere between the brazilian and the person playing monopoly##7
 7. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5
 9. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
10. the person playing poker is in an even position##4
11. the person playing bridge is on the far right##1
12. the brazilian is on the right of the indonesian##1
13. the chinese is somewhere to the right of the person playing poker##5
14. the thai is on the left of the nigerian##1
15. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the left of the chinese##5
