 4. the person who likes turquise is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is golf##5
 6. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 7. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
 8. the person who likes orange is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##5
 9. the person who likes apricot is the person who's sport is sailing##1
10. the person who likes mauve is the person who's sport is rowing##1
11. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the person who likes coral##3
12. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
13. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left##1
14. the person who likes chestnut is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
15. the person who's sport is cricket is in an odd position##4
16. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##5
17. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
18. the person who likes orange is somewhere to the left of the person who likes turquise##5
